name: Reinita °_°
description:
Sun shines on you /
you color of the sky /
A sunset in the tropics /
A flamingo in the rain /
A peacock at play.

On the ground you are a rooster /
In the air you are a dove.

You Queen of the Wild
Naranja, little-queen
